      • parseClassAndPropDef

        public static ArgListParser.ParseTree parseClassAndPropDef(java.lang.String input)
                                                    throws ArgListTokenizer.ParseException
        Constructs a new ListTokenizer around input and then calls parseClassAndPropDef(). This class assumes it can read and parse the whole string, otherwise it throws a ArgListTokenizer.ParseException.
        参数:
        input - The input string to parse.
        返回:
        The
        抛出:
        ArgListTokenizer.ParseException
